data.description: One of a kind 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in desired neighborhood!! This home is beautifully updated & move in ready. So many extras that set this home apart! Luxury wood laminate & tile flooring throughout, fresh neutral interior paint, crown molding, remodeled kitchen with custom vent hood, open shelving, & granite counters, large stack stone fireplace in living room, & updated bathrooms inside the home. Walk out back and take in the mountain views in the large yard with gazebo, garden area, & huge storage shed/workshop. Bring your toys! Extra parking on side of driveway & RV double gate.
